@MemberShip.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5156

### Login to get access token
POST {{MemberShip.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@baseauth.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Create Role with Permissions - Test 1 (Simple)
POST {{MemberShip.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Role 1",
  "description": "Test role with read permissions",
  "permissionIds": [1, 6, 13]
}

### Create Role with Permissions - Test 2 (Multiple)
POST {{MemberShip.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Role 2",
  "description": "Test role with multiple permissions",
  "permissionIds": [1, 2, 3, 6, 7, 8, 13, 14]
}

### Create Role with Permissions - Test 3 (Single)
POST {{MemberShip.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Role 3",
  "description": "Test role with single permission",
  "permissionIds": [1]
}

### Create Role with Permissions - Test 4 (Empty)
POST {{MemberShip.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Role 4",
  "description": "Test role without permissions",
  "permissionIds": []
}

### Get All Roles
GET {{MemberShip.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get All Permissions
GET {{MemberShip.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
